author: Sherpa_536
attribution_text: Freshwater West by Sherpa_536 (CC BY 2.0)
description:
Around the Pembrokeshire Coast, there are several little bus routes connecting all of the little villages together. The service is 1.5 hours duration, but it is an enjoyable ride (especially in lovely weather).

Here is Optare Solo YJ10 EXU coming through Freshwater West on the 4th June 2013. This vehicle is operated by Silcox's of Pembroke Dock.
